Introduction

Yubin is a South Korean singer-songwriter, composer, and rapper currently under rrr Entertainment and Wild Entertainment Group. She is a former member of the girl group Wonder Girls.

In 2007, Yubin was set to debut as a member of Five Girls, a five-member girl group under Good Entertainment.

However, due to financial issues, the group was disbanded before they could debut. Other members of Five Girls included UEE, G.NA, Hyoseong and Jiwon.

She made her solo debut on June 5, 2018, with her first single "Dosiyeoja".
